
STEP 0  :  Init Project RN

npx react-native init AwesomeProject

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

STEP 1  :  Install React Navigation

npm install @react-navigation/native
npm install react-native-reanimated react-native-gesture-handler react-native-screens react-native-safe-area-context @react-native-community/masked-view
npm install @react-navigation/stack

for ios : 
cd ios; pod install; cd ..

for android : 
add this code on app/build.gradle
implementation 'androidx.appcompat:appcompat:1.1.0-rc01'
implementation 'androidx.swiperefreshlayout:swiperefreshlayout:1.1.0-alpha02'

reference : https://reactnavigation.org/docs/hello-react-navigation/

check this libs its work --> look App.js

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

STEP 2  :  Install Native Base

npm install native-base --save
react-native link

reference : https://docs.nativebase.io/docs/GetStarted.html

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

STEP 3  :  Foldering

add folder src/screen
add per screen etc : splash, login, home

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

STEP 4 :
npm install @react-navigation/native @react-navigation/compat
npm install @react-navigation/bottom-tabs

pod install

npm install axios